- install VBox
- install kubectl (managing the cluster):
snap install kubectl --classic
- install minicube (creation single-node cluster):
https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/

+ set default driver: minikube config set driver virtualbox
+ start cluster: minikube start 
- minikube start --cpus=4 --memory=8gb --disk-size=25gb
+ config: ~/.kube/config
+ files: ~/.minikube
+ iso: .minikube/machines/minikube/boot2docker.iso
+ cluster status: kubectl get componentstatuses
+ cluster info: kubectl cluster-info
+ quantity of nodes: kubectl get nodes
+ stop cluster: minikube stop => will stop vbox machine
+ delete cluster: minikube delete
+ minikube ssh: will connect as docker user
+ kubectl get nodes

